export const strings = {
    prefixAgo: 'il y a',
    prefixFromNow: 'd\'ici',
    seconds: 'moins d\'une minute',
    minute: 'une minute',
    minutes: '%d minutes',
    hour: 'une heure',
    hours: '%d heures',
    day: 'un jour',
    days: '%d jours',
    month: 'un mois',
    months: '%d mois',
    year: 'un an',
    years: '%d ans',
};
